{"tid":290286,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony X3000 交流區","createTime":"2017-06-19T15:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T19:16:38.000Z","uid":119709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"183b471b4d094aa07b0f976a300114d496414594","tid":290286,"uid":119709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:57:29.000Z","msg":"明明見到唔少人入左手<br />\n但咁耐都無人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家用左咁耐有無啲咩問題岀現左？<br />\n有咩配件必買？<br />\n打算入手穩定器 但仲未決定買邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0df5a55c779fbde5d9bc791f9f09c7e1509b63","tid":290286,"uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T16:29:58.000Z","msg":"用過去兩次旅行 <br />\n4K 片好清好穩 完全唔洗穩定器 拎住跑都得 <br />\n舊電去得好快就真 但有用Sony prosumer 既話舊電係完全一樣所以我有成三舊電<br />\n<br />\n色水非常討好 <br />\n<br />\n夜間noise 比較明顯<br />\n<br />\n但冇咩投訴了 3.2k有咁既質素<br />\nBtw 個remote 好撚柒"},{"pid":"1b7812730a243b1c91e5df658abba53ca2587d34","tid":290286,"uid":16552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"用家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍4k d電去得好快下, 同埋散熱真心唔好<br />\n熄一熄機降一降溫, d電會多番1格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買多兩粒電先得, 我本身用rx100m5所以可以share用<br />\n<br />\n防震手持行路就真係ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係單車上手持就好震下...可能用mount會好d<br />\n轉去影相都可以接受, 你當係廣角版iphone就冇投訴<br />\n<br />\nbtw我成日唔記得個mon係防水定防濺水.....有冇人可以話我知?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n部機我就sure只係防濺水, 因為要加潛水殼先真係防水<br />\n<br />\nmount就手持連mon位果個我最常用, 冇買穩定器....都想買番個好似自拍神棍果種mount,<br />\n可以伸出d果種, 咁拍片就拍到全身,<br />\n如果唔係就咁手持就都係拍到半身only, <br />\n唔知其他巴打有冇好推介呢?"},{"pid":"e5d466445871622ddd509014402439c13e1ce1eb","tid":290286,"uid":17980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:16:29.000Z","msg":"x1000加三軸上手科技留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134890ed38b82a02935c16bb831a7f41f441c738","tid":290286,"uid":16552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:10:11.000Z","msg":"x3000r 既防震好似係暫時最top, <br />\nx1000會少一兩級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ba0ef82e18bf902da208daf72b9b7955b2dd99","tid":290286,"uid":100176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:21:28.000Z","msg":"其實個remote係咪哂9氣？<br />\n淨機係邊到買巴打們？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccf270ff02e9ad0a0413c99cf53d8673cb732c1","tid":290286,"uid":54871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:22:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0d4fad6534217dfa8f04766d0fa6fb521471f06","tid":290286,"uid":16552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T10:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實個remote係咪哂9氣？<br />\n淨機係邊到買巴打們？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係wor, <br />\n有個mon live view都幾好使好用"},{"pid":"e42bbbc65899188a6c0dba2cfb366aeb3c2702fd","tid":290286,"uid":54871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:04:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc1cddf0c0413235344c378039af28063a78e1e3","tid":290286,"uid":16552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實個remote係咪哂9氣？<br />\n淨機係邊到買巴打們？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係wor, <br />\n有個mon live view都幾好使好用</blockquote><br />\n個指扣果個accessory 好似幾正</blockquote><br />\n我最常用呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4f093d7d08a4657aad62b9495b7ff13999e143","tid":290286,"uid":54871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017